# TASKS

Use this board to coordinate manual handoff between planner, implementer, and reviewer.

Status values:
- `in_planning`
- `ready_for_implement`
- `in_implementation`
- `ready_for_review`
- `in_review`
{{- if eq .Workflow "auto"}}
- `in_testing`
- `test_passed`
- `test_failed`
{{- end}}
- `changes_requested`
- `done`

Command expectations:
- planner moves tasks into `in_planning` and `ready_for_implement`
- implementer moves tasks into `in_implementation` and `ready_for_review`, and resumes work from `changes_requested`
{{- if eq .Workflow "auto"}}
- reviewer moves tasks into `in_review`, `in_testing`, or `changes_requested`
- tester moves tasks into `in_testing`, `test_passed`, or `test_failed`
{{- else}}
- reviewer moves tasks into `in_review`, `done`, or `changes_requested`
{{- end}}
- `status_cycle` should report deterministic task status, current owner role, and next recommended action based on this board

